title: Imagine a place...
text: ...where you can belong to a school club, a gaming group, or a worldwide art community. Where just you and a handful of friends can spend time together. A place that makes it easy to talk every day and hang out more often.
text2: Discord servers are organized into topic-based channels where you can collaborate, share, and just talk about your day without clogging up a group chat.
text3: Grab a seat in a voice channel when you’re free. Friends in your server can see you’re around and instantly pop in to talk without having to call.
text4: Get any community running with moderation tools and custom member access. Give members special powers, set up private channels, and more.
text5: Low-latency voice and video feels like you’re in the same room. Wave hello over video, watch friends stream their games, or gather up and have a drawing session with screen share.
heading1: Create an invite-only place where you belong
